voidc.label: voidc.zip - Void Town
voidc.title: Void Town
voidc.description: Smallish city/realism map with a few new textures. The map source is included.
voidc.author: nolcoz

volcano.label: volcano.zip - Eruption is immanent!
volcano.title: Eruption is immanent!
volcano.description: Very small temple built around a volcano. A deathmatch level with single player settings, but no exit (only a message). Barely average.
volcano.author: Trace Stuart

vr.label: vr.zip - Virtual Reality Quake
vr.title: Virtual Reality Quake
vr.description:
"No Shooting Is Allowed In This Module. - Sneak past the guards." Rather dull as you can simply rush through the rooms.
This file was repackaged by Spirit. You can find the original .zip in the trash
vr.author: George Grotans

vrkcoop1.label: vrkcoop1.zip - Forever Lost
vrkcoop1.title: Forever Lost
vrkcoop1.description: Around medium-sized blue puzzle dungeon made for cooperative play (cannot be completed solo).
vrkcoop1.author: VuRkka

vrksp1.label: vrksp1.zip - Blackened Call
vrksp1.title: Blackened Call
vrksp1.description:
Small Metal/runic level.

Note: This map requires a source port with increased limits.
vrksp1.author: VuRkka

w_temple.label: w_temple.zip - Windy Temple
w_temple.title: Windy Temple
w_temple.description: A small map featuring some sort of floating structure. The author's first Quake map.
w_temple.author: Lukasxd

walhalla.label: walhalla.zip - The Fate for Walhalla
walhalla.title: The Fate for Walhalla
walhalla.description: Large map with mixed texture styles, many traps and some puzzles.
walhalla.author: Tobias Reichert

warehaus.label: warehaus.zip - The Warehouse
warehaus.title: The Warehouse
warehaus.description: Medium sized base map with a slightly above id-level amount of unaligned textures and some oddly scaled crates.
warehaus.author: Taskmaster (Warren Marshall)

warpgate.label: warpgate.zip - The Warpgate
warpgate.title: The Warpgate
warpgate.description: Medium sized Wizard map with a sense of exploration.
warpgate.author: Ozric

warpspasm.label: warpspasm.zip - Warp Spasm
warpspasm.title: Warp Spasm
warpspasm.description:
Probably the most evil and hostile atmosphere a Quake release ever had. This episode is built upon Quoth code and monsters. It comes with "dark ambient" music which adds to the feeling. The levels are huge, and the number of monsters in each one is extreme. An essential release, but clearly not for everyone.

Note: This episode requires Quoth and an engine port with raised limits. A modified version of GLQuake is included.
warpspasm.author: ijed

watertor.label: watertor.zip - Water Torture
watertor.title: Water Torture
watertor.description: Small brick map with upward/downward water tubes.
watertor.author: Benjamin S. Clower

watrways.label: watrways.zip - Waterways
watrways.title: Waterways
watrways.description: Small and very dark level consisting of two rooms connected by a drain pipe, possibly designed for deathmatch.
watrways.author: Unknown

watrwrks1_1.label: watrwrks1_1.zip - Waterworks
watrwrks1_1.title: Waterworks
watrwrks1_1.description: Medium sized blue brick cistern map with pipes and a Base bit.
watrwrks1_1.author: Erik Robson

wca.label: wca.zip - Weird comic art Quake
wca.title: Weird comic art Quake
wca.description: Small to medium sized blue brick map. Very basic in terms of looks and gameplay, however there are many original machines, animated bits and mapobjects. Some funny features here, worth a look for sure.
wca.author: K.S.

weaponf.label: weaponf.zip - The Weapon Factory
weaponf.title: The Weapon Factory
weaponf.description: Small Base map - a weapon factory producing aircrafts, tanks and submarines. Neat idea, but poorly executed.
weaponf.author: EraserX

well.label: well.zip - The Well of Lost Souls
well.title: The Well of Lost Souls
well.description: Medium sized metal/wizard level with a few traps.
well.author: Michael Reed

welloflostsouls_repack.label: welloflostsouls_repack.zip - Well of Lost Souls
welloflostsouls_repack.title: Well of Lost Souls
welloflostsouls_repack.description:
Small to medium-sized map inspired by E4M2- The Tower of Despair.
[repacked for Quaddicted]
welloflostsouls_repack.author: Miss Bubbles

wetbase.label: wetbase.zip - Wetbase
wetbase.title: Wetbase
wetbase.description: Large space base with many custom textures. There are many potentially interesting bits one may expect to find in a base like this, such as officers quarters, mess hall, kitchen, and generator rooms, however, the choice of textures and style is often quite odd.
wetbase.author: Andy Baird

whippet.label: whippet.zip - Eat this...
whippet.title: Eat this...
whippet.description: Small medieval/metal level with a rocky outdoor area. Includes the .map file and a demo.
whippet.author: Marc Roussel

whirlq01.label: whirlq01.zip - Adrift
whirlq01.title: Adrift
whirlq01.description:
Small abstact blue void map using custom textures. The texture wad is included.

Note: This map requires Arcane Dimensions 1.7.
whirlq01.author: whirledtsar

whiteroom.label: whiteroom.zip - White Room
whiteroom.title: White Room
whiteroom.description:
Medium sized base map with a unique concept: "keep the usual shapes but take away the textures." A biohazard outbreak at this facility adds lots of blood to the mostly white textures.
This file was repackaged by Spirit. You can find the original .zip in the trash
whiteroom.author: Willem (Warren Marshall)

wieder.label: wieder.zip - Timebomb & Salvation
wieder.title: Timebomb & Salvation
wieder.description:
Two maps: a small unfinished base level (timebomb), and a small metal level with extremely nasty traps (salv). Salvation is a "love it or hate it" map, save often and try some of the usual secret finding techniques to finish it. Both require the SOA pack.

The "nice" rating is for Salvation, Timebomb seems Average.
wieder.author: Charlie Wiederhold

winbbcoh.label: winbbcoh.zip - Barbican Of Hell
winbbcoh.title: Barbican Of Hell
winbbcoh.description: Small runic level. The map source is included.
winbbcoh.author: Windaws

wind.label: wind.zip - Valley of the wind
wind.title: Valley of the wind
wind.description:
Two medium sized, boxed maps with a story and cutscenes. The base bit sucks, the wizard parts are so-and-so.
Only just OKish.
wind.author: Steve Wilson (Thundermug)

winterpack2005-2006.label: winterpack2005-2006.zip - winterpack2005-2006
winterpack2005-2006.title: winterpack2005-2006
winterpack2005-2006.description: Two maps build from the scraps of other mappers: Hrimfaxi used Drew's scraps for a large egyptian/mayan map called "Egyptian rhapsody!" Zwiffle used czg's for a ikblue map called "Teacups - are my intentions".
winterpack2005-2006.author: Hrimfaxi (Drew), Zwiffle (czg)

wishes.label: wishes.zip - The Well of Wishes
wishes.title: The Well of Wishes
wishes.description: Medium sized, interconnected and largely nonlinear Metal map. Very nice.
wishes.author: Rick Lipsey

wishwell.label: wishwell.zip - The Wishing Well
wishwell.title: The Wishing Well
wishwell.description: Small to medium horizontal Wizard with different texture combinations is each room. Features Willy the Spider.
wishwell.author: Tom Cleghorn aka Murgatroyd

woa_kayne.label: woa_kayne.zip - Wrath of Ahnkii
woa_kayne.title: Wrath of Ahnkii
woa_kayne.description:
Large Egyptian-style map. Comes with a custom skybox and a music track. The map source is included.

Note: This map requires a source port with increased limits.
An updated version is available here.
woa_kayne.author: Kayne

wolf3d.label: wolf3d.zip - Wolf3D
wolf3d.title: Wolf3D
wolf3d.description: E1M1 of Wolfenstein 3D, complete with original textures and confusing layout. Uses some SOA entities. For die-hard retro fans.
wolf3d.author: Daryl Deep

wolfie3d.label: wolfie3d.zip - Wolfenstein3D e1m1
wolfie3d.title: Wolfenstein3D e1m1
wolfie3d.description: Extremely bad conversion of Wolfenstein3D's first map.
wolfie3d.author: Rutabaga

wtot.label: wtot.zip - Welcome to Ogre tower
wtot.title: Welcome to Ogre tower
wtot.description: Very small metal tower with a crusher trap.
wtot.author: Dick Nelson

xalanoth.label: xalanoth.zip - Xala'noth - Part 1
xalanoth.title: Xala'noth - Part 1
xalanoth.description:
Medium-sized level using GothicDM and Knave textures and featuring strong colored lighting. It comes with a start map, a custom skybox and a music track by the author.

Note: This map requires Arcane Dimensions 1.70+ and a source port with increased limits.
Cannot be run from the Quake Injector!
xalanoth.author: Remilia Scarlet

xl2.label: xl2.zip - The Citadel of Sinners
xl2.title: The Citadel of Sinners
xl2.description:
Very large fortress/citadel with many corridors and ambushes. Comes with a small skill selection map.

Note: This map requires a source port with increased limits.
[Does not work with the Quake Injector]
xl2.author: xlarve

xl3.label: xl3.zip - The Subconscious Fear
xl3.title: The Subconscious Fear
xl3.description:
Large 'techno-dungeon' with many corridors and ambushes.

[Does not work with the Quake Injector]
xl3.author: xlarve

xl4.label: xl4.zip - The Sector Four
xl4.title: The Sector Four
xl4.description:
Huge base map, a labyrinth of tight corridors with ambushes.

Note: This map requires a source port with increased limits
[Cannot be run through the Quake Injector]
xl4.author: xLarve

xld.label: xld.zip - xlarve's dream
xld.title: xlarve's dream
xld.description:
Large Metal/runic/mixed-tex dungeon with relentless arena combat in small rooms and tight corridors. 500+ monsters in total.

Note: This map requires an engine port with increased limits.
xld.author: xlarve

xmasjam2018.label: xmasjam2018.zip - Xmas Jam 2018 - 1024³ theme
xmasjam2018.title: Xmas Jam 2018 - 1024³ theme
xmasjam2018.description:
Annual Xmas mapping event. This pack features 21 small maps in varied styles where all gameplay takes place within a 1024x1024x1024 space. It includes a start map and is powered by the Arcane Dimensions devkit + some additional content. The map sources are included as well.

Note: These maps require a source port with increased limits
(screenshot courtesy of sock)
xmasjam2018.author: Bal, Bloodshot, Ing, ionous, Ish, JCR, Krampus, Naitelveni, negke, Pinchy Skree, Qmaster, Queenjazz, Rhoq, Scampie, Shambler, Shotro, Spipper, Strideh

xmasjam2019.label: xmasjam2019.zip - Xmas Jam 2019
xmasjam2019.title: Xmas Jam 2019
xmasjam2019.description:
Annual Christmas mapping event. This pack features 17 small maps in varied styles where all gameplay takes place within a 1024x1024x1024 space. It includes a start map and is powered by the Arcane Dimensions devkit (included) + some additional content. The map sources are included as well.

Note: These maps require a source port with increased limits
xmasjam2019.author: Chedap, Comrade Beep, Fairweather, Glans, Greenwood, Heresy, ionous, JCR, MortalMaxx, Naitelveni, Nolcoz, Nyoei, onetruepurple, Pinchy, Qalten, Shadesmaster

xnq1002.label: xnq1002.zip - Centurion
xnq1002.title: Centurion
xnq1002.description: A fairly large canyon with several Q2base buildings. Originally started as a 100brush map, it eventually turned into a 'proper' map. Map source is included.
xnq1002.author: XeNoN

xnsm2_se.bsp.label: xnsm2_se.bsp.zip - Realm of the tetris overlord
xnsm2_se.bsp.title: Realm of the tetris overlord
xnsm2_se.bsp.description:
A few tweaks and improvements made to sm9_xenon, including better lighting, gameplay and detailing.
Small but nice map in q3gothic flavour.
xnsm2_se.bsp.author: Rich "xen" Thorne

xplore.label: xplore.zip - Explore or Die
xplore.title: Explore or Die
xplore.description: Around medium sized base map with Cr8 textures and somewhat non-linear gameplay relying on exploration (for ammo). Comes with a custom skybox and support for colored lighting.
xplore.author: Speedy

zanthu.label: zanthu.zip - Castle Zanthu
zanthu.title: Castle Zanthu
zanthu.description:
Medium-sized castle using Daikatana E3 textures. Comes with a custom skybox and a poster screenshot.

Note: This map requires a source port with increased limits.
zanthu.author: Greenwood

zendar1d.label: zendar1d.zip - The Horde of Zendar
zendar1d.title: The Horde of Zendar
zendar1d.description:
Large medieval city at nighttime with a strong focus on exploration and route choices. It comes with custom medieval-style items. The map source is included in the PAK.

Note: This map requires an engine port with increased limits.
zendar1d.author: sock

zer.label: zer.zip - Zerstörer - Testament of the Destroyer
zer.title: Zerstörer - Testament of the Destroyer
zer.description:
"Be very scared... Zerstörer is here to destroy you, and is arguably the meanest Q1 SP episode around. A 7-map partial conversion with excellent new graphics and superb effects, cool weapons and interesting monsters. The maps are varied and continually interesting, but Zerstörer is really outstanding for the amazing atmosphere: bleak, inhospitable, and often truly scary. Very creative, very engrossing - again, unmissable."
-TEAMShambler

Additional files: patch 1.1, zerend hotfix, teaser demo.
zer.author: Nihilism Unlimited

zerdem.label: zerdem.zip - Zerstörer Demo
zerdem.title: Zerstörer Demo
zerdem.description: A short non-interactive demo setting the tone of the events about to unfold in Zerstörer - Testament of the Destroyer.
zerdem.author: Nihilism Unlimited

zertm_pack.label: zertm_pack.zip - Zerstörer Turtlemap Pack
zertm_pack.title: Zerstörer Turtlemap Pack
zertm_pack.description:
A pack of turtlemaps for the Zerstörer mod made by efdat, HeadThump and neg!ke.

  • Love in a bunker, baby! by efdat

  • Hold of the Troglodyte by HeadThump

  • Aderlass by neg!ke
zertm_pack.author: efdat, HeadThump, negke

zjam1.label: zjam1.zip - Zombie Jam 1
zjam1.title: Zombie Jam 1
zjam1.description: Results of an impromptu speedmapping/jam session following a "medieval E1M2 style brickwork and about 20 monsters" theme. The map sources are included.
zjam1.author: mukor, sock, Zombie

zjam2.label: zjam2.zip - Zombie Jam 2
zjam2.title: Zombie Jam 2
zjam2.description: Results of an impromptu speedmapping/jam session following a "lifts and zombies and 20ish monsters" theme. The map sources are included.
zjam2.author: Giftmacher, mukor, scar3crow, sock, Zombie

zoom9.label: zoom9.zip - ZOOM9
zoom9.title: ZOOM9
zoom9.description:
First place in a competition of the Russian magazine Game.exe.
Small base map with modified monsters, custom level mechanics and a few new sound effects.
zoom9.author: Andrew Aksenov

zsp1.label: zsp1.zip - Perversion of Gun
zsp1.title: Perversion of Gun
zsp1.description: "Pretty awful, dark, cramped, linear base/metal map, using Cr8_Set tex." - Fairly small and dull lighting, but nice design.
zsp1.author: Zwiffle

zwifflesm1.label: zwifflesm1.zip - Geometric Map of Horror
zwifflesm1.title: Geometric Map of Horror
zwifflesm1.description: Some speedmap with Q3A textures by Zwiffle.
zwifflesm1.author: Zwiffle
